    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331060/extras/db3058a6276e9fbfa982492a1d57f47c.poster.avif?t=1764608167\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331060/extras/db3058a6276e9fbfa982492a1d57f47c.webm?t=1764608167\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331060/extras/db3058a6276e9fbfa982492a1d57f47c.mp4?t=1764608167\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331060/extras/42465c1e9bb2a3e0aac268b24207ad6c.webp?t=1764608167\" width=600 height=40 /></span><br><br>《Gambit Shifter》这款益智游戏风格静雅，适合国际象棋的各类棋手体验，高手与新人咸宜。<br><br>手执一枚棋子，走过道道关卡，每一着都需要仔细斟酌。<br>变换棋形，解锁各种步法，一路走到最后，拿下敌王！ <br><br>游戏包含80多道手工制作的关卡，原创音乐助你专注，即使不懂国际象棋也不妨碍体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331060/extras/79001b80a92f4a2857d3b00eaab3c8d2.webp?t=1764608167\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331060/extras/1c0070d14fb3b38fe06aaf11f9e11159.poster.avif?t=1764608167\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331060/extras/1c0070d14fb3b38fe06aaf11f9e11159.webm?t=1764608167\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331060/extras/1c0070d14fb3b38fe06aaf11f9e11159.mp4?t=1764608167\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>教程简短，容易上手，直接带你走进游戏世界，80多道关卡各不相同，多种谜题等你破解。探索缤纷多彩的地形，考验你的策略思维。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331060/extras/1b3b8d5084e6a163af5187d1726a97d5.webp?t=1764608167\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331060/extras/b1d8d340b4e1951f6cec4d04dc54e18e.poster.avif?t=1764608167\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331060/extras/b1d8d340b4e1951f6cec4d04dc54e18e.webm?t=1764608167\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331060/extras/b1d8d340b4e1951f6cec4d04dc54e18e.mp4?t=1764608167\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>通过一定关卡之后，你将发现新的机制，例如移动平台乃至秘密通道。活用战术，突破层层障碍，最终直取敌王！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331060/extras/c89fa93bc4b6b55dedecce8c0ea34017.webp?t=1764608167\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331060/extras/f3405aa41089c7da14bce02a853149f0.poster.avif?t=1764608167\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331060/extras/f3405aa41089c7da14bce02a853149f0.webm?t=1764608167\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331060/extras/f3405aa41089c7da14bce02a853149f0.mp4?t=1764608167\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>80多个关卡均为手工制作</strong>。<br></li><li><strong>手执一枚兵</strong>，运用智慧吃下敌王！<br></li><li>犯了一个错误？您可以随时撤销您的动作！<br></li><li><strong>游戏世界闲适多彩</strong>，国际象棋的高手与新人咸宜！<br></li><li><strong>原创音乐</strong>可以助你专心解谜。</li></ul><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331060/extras/04253921b7f16744fd2cce2871ce5723.avif?t=1764608167\" width=600 height=138 /></span>",
